/-- The `G` representation `C(G, rep)` given a representation `rep`.
The `G` action is defined by `g ‚Ä¢ f := x ‚Ü¶ g ‚Ä¢ f (g‚Åª¬π * x)`. -/
abbrev Iobj (rep : Action (TopModuleCat R) G) : Action (TopModuleCat R) G where
  V := .of R C(G, rep.V)
